  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们来梳理一下inky-mbta-tracker的架构。核心是一个子图，里面包含schedule and prediction workers、queue processor，还有一个队列本身。workers负责拉取MBTA的实时数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inky-mbta-tracker",
        "schedule and prediction workers",
        "queue processor",
        "queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "workers和processor都跟队列有交互对吧？workers是往队列里写数据，processor是从队列里取？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "schedule and prediction workers",
        "queue processor",
        "queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，workers把预测数据推到队列，processor消费队列。另外processor要输出到两个地方：Redis和MQTT。Redis用圆柱形表示，MQTT用bow-rect形状。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "queue processor",
        "Redis",
        "MQTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，子图和内部三个节点已画好，processor到Redis和MQTT的连接也加上了。consumer端呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inky-mbta-tracker",
        "schedule and prediction workers",
        "queue",
        "queue processor",
        "Redis",
        "MQTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两个consumer。一个是inky-display，用curv-trap形状，它从Redis读取数据；另一个是Home Assistant，用斜矩形，从MQTT订阅。注意display和Redis之间标注\"reads\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inky-display",
        "Redis",
        "Home Assistant",
        "MQTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。Home Assistant到MQTT的连接也标了\"reads\"吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "inky-display",
        "Home Assistant",
        "Redis",
        "MQTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，workers到queue、processor到queue这两条线还没画。workers和processor都要连到queue，但不用标注文字。",
